<br>
Starting over on the new server is going to be very hard compared to re-rolling on an established (old) server.  No KEI, no easy to find rez'es, no cheap gear nor weapons of any kind.  Leveling is going to be slower.  Twink buffs and gear makes a huge difference in reducing down time and death.<br>
<br>
