There have been discussions here about proceeding to the tougher areas without going through those steps. <br>
<br>
I still see the need to go through the Kunark content, the Planes (Hate and such)  simply to get the equipment and some spells. Probably also go through Ntov before VT, Seru, and then up to PoP. <br>
